+-----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+
|   256 doubles array   |       **1.00**       |         1.02         |         1.08         |         1.03         |         6.76         |         7.34         |         6.88         |         3.89         |
+-----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+
|   256 unicode array   |         1.00         |         0.89         |         0.89         |         0.91         |         0.56         |         0.73         |         0.83         |       **0.47**       |
+-----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+
