~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

+-----------------------+-----------------------+-----------------------+-----------------------+-----------------------+-----------------------+-----------------------+-----------------------+-----------------------+
|      deserialize      |   ``loads()``\ [9]_   | ``Decoder()``\ [10]_  |  ``loads(n)``\ [11]_  | ``Decoder(n)``\ [12]_ |         ujson         |      simplejson       |        stdlib         |         yajl          |
+=======================+=======================+=======================+=======================+=======================+=======================+=======================+=======================+=======================+
|    100 arrays dict    |         1.00          |         1.00          |         0.90          |       **0.90**        |         0.95          |         1.60          |         1.11          |         1.18          |
+-----------------------+-----------------------+-----------------------+-----------------------+-----------------------+-----------------------+-----------------------+-----------------------+-----------------------+
